Package: bage
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Estimation and Forecasting of Age-Specific Rates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "John",
             family = "Bryant",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "john@bayesiandemography.com"),
      person(given = "Junni",
             family = "Zhang",
             role = "aut",
             email = "junni@bayesiandemography.com"))
Description: Bayesian estimation and forecasting of age-specific
    rates, probabilities, and means. Uses singular value
    decompositions and the package TMB (Template Model Builder),
    to make the estimation and forecasting scalable and fast.
